	<div id="id5c2" class="post">
		<h2 class="title"><span class="image-wrapper"><img height="45" alt="I knew I liked brownies" width="350" class="title" src="../../../resources/net.databinder.components.RenderedLabel/e630cce"/><span class="title">I knew I liked brownies</span></span></h2>
		<div class="byline"><span>
			<span>By <span class="alias">Leland</span>, <span>on March 18, 2007</span></span>
			<span id="id5c3" class="tags">
					{&nbsp;<span><a href="../../../eat/tag/baking/#selected-tag"><span>baking</span></a></span>&nbsp;}
			</span>
		</span></div>
		<div><p>The only way for me to understand the difference between the three brownies I&#8217;ve made in the last few months is to view them in a convenient table format.</p>


